  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House",
    "asOf": "2019-11-18",
    "date": "2021-01-13T13:59:32Z",
    "text": "Reforming Disaster Recovery Act of 2019\n\nThis bill provides statutory authority for certain procedures related to the Community Development Block Grant - Disaster Recovery (CDBR-DR) Program and adds new program requirements, including with respect to coordination of benefits, precertification for grant assistance, and allocation of grant funds. Additionally, the bill expands CDBG-DR assistance to Puerto Rico.\n\nFinally, the bill establishes the Community Development Block Grant Disaster Recovery Reserve Fund."
  },
